-- MOVES-Schroders appoints senior advisers to multi-asset business
-- 
-- Mon Sep 29, 2014 12:15PM EDT
-- None



Sept 29 (Reuters) - London-based asset management company Schroders Plc <SDR.L> appointed two university professors as senior advisers for its multi-asset unit.

Duncan Shand is a professor at the Warwick Business School at the University of Warwick, England.